  RunHaven v0.5.0  Step 4/4: Confirm launch
  Final check before launch.

  Agent       antigravity
  Network     provider allowlist
  Boundary    /workspace only
  Host home   not mounted
  Credentials not mounted by default

  Press Enter to prepare launch. RunHaven starts it after restoring the terminal.

  Exact command
  container run --rm --init --name runhaven-antigravity-snapshot-run --read-only --mount
  type=bind,source=/selected-workspace,target=/workspace --network runhaven-provider runhaven/antigravity:0.1.0
  antigravity

  esc goes back. enter confirms. q quits.
